汽车行业都是最高的，汽车毛利率是蔚来汽车的近 2 倍。 李斌还指出，特斯拉在中国市场的降价是其面临激烈竞争采取的一种方法。「特斯拉的 Model S 和 Model X 其实打不了什么价格战，因为它的成本在那，但 Mode3 和 ModelY 是个光板车，本身就是成本很低的车。」李斌指出，在这种情况下，随着比亚迪等中国同行的崛起，特斯拉的价格战也是不得已而为之，恰恰证明了中国品牌做得好。 「它在美国有定价权，因为有百分之六七十的份额，但它在中国只有百分之六七的份额，不到 10%。」李斌表示，蔚来肯定不会跟风降价，因为和特斯拉本就不在一个市场。其指出，作为车企应该思考给用户到底创造了什么价值，用最低的价格去获得最好的产品和服务，经济理论上是不成立的。李斌：蔚来毛利率低参与不了「价格战」，特斯拉在中国不具定价权 - 经济观察网 － 专业财经新闻网站"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-de1ecfede60bb24fd4ff7b8f1a5b112d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "12 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593457922"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4ImefE5qWq6qUgEAMaCDk0MTYxMjE1IOyMqaEGMAE4ZEAgcgk1OTM0NTc5MjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1680804360.9009118", "card_id": "Q_593814050", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 193}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人需要独处吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-cc50650cce12ebbd8e9c62e04909f293_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "11 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593814050"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ImefE5qWq6qUgEAMaCDk0MjQwMjE5IPPctKEGMAI4hwJAIXIJNTkzODE0MDUweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1680804360.9013624", "card_id": "Q_585771205", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "备考公务员需要注意什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-54f66087b3fe39e4d34dbab9f826103f_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "11 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"